dataIdInfo.idPurp: This toolset packages the Raster Soil Survey products, the exported tabular text files from NASIS with the raster file as a File Geodatabase with a gSSURGO template and as a SSURGO Download package.
dataIdInfo.idAbs: This tool was developed for Regional GIS Specialists in the Soil and Plant Science Division to prepare Raster Soil Surveys for staging.
